summaries.short: As survivors open up to Farrow and his producer Rich McHugh, NBC pulls back on the story – and becomes entangled in its own scandal.​
summaries.full: Farrow's former producer Rich McHugh sheds light on their experience at NBC News, exploring the process of interviewing numerous sources on camera – including Rose McGowan, who accused a yet unnamed movie mogul of rape – and their gradual realization that the story was being shut down behind the scenes.
